# Networking

- URLSession async/await; no third-party HTTP in v1
- Generic APIClient: request<T: Decodable>(_ endpoint) async throws -> T
- Endpoint enum/struct for type-safe paths
- Per-instance base URL and API key injection
- Map URLError, HTTP status, DecodingError to AppError
- Self-signed certs: URLSessionDelegate for server trust
